      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:03:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反弹停滞之际中国誓言加强股市监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/china-vows-to-tighten-stock-market-supervision-to-control-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国务院在周五发布的新指引中誓言收紧股票上市标准，并敦促企业改善公司治理，这是支撑股市的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/china-vows-to-tighten-stock-market-supervision-to-control-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 07:51:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国央行李承晚表示可能降息，逐步走向中性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/bok-keeps-rate-on-hold-opting-for-steady-stance-after-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行行长李昌镛表示，如果通胀压力如预期缓解，今年晚些时候可能会降息，与全球政策制定者一起开辟政策宽松之路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/bok-keeps-rate-on-hold-opting-for-steady-stance-after-polls</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 00:52:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
